5. \u041e\u0433\u0440\u043e\u043c\u043d\u044b\u0435 \u0441\u0438\u043b\u044b \u0438 \u0440\u0435\u0441\u0443\u0440\u0441\u044b \u0431\u0440\u043e\u0448\u0435\u043d\u044b \u043d\u0430 \u043d\u0430\u0448\u0435 \u0443\u043d\u0438\u0447\u0442\u043e\u0436\u0435\u043d\u0438\u0435\" |trans-title=Roman Zaitsev: For the Kremlin, we are a bone in the throat. Enormous efforts and resources are left to our destruction. |publisher=[[Fakty i Kommentarii]] |date=2015-04-11 |accessdate=2016-04-20 |language=Russian |df=dmy-all}}</ref><ref name=\"UNIAN\">{{cite web|url=http://www.unian.info/politics/1334486-luhansk-governor-tuka-dismissed-media.html|title=Luhansk Governor Tuka dismissed \u2013 media : UNIAN news|publisher=[[UNIAN]] |date=2016-04-29 |accessdate=2016-05-13 |language=English |df=dmy-all}}</ref><ref name=\"kyivpost\">{{cite web|url=http://www.kyivpost.com/article/content/ukraine-politics/poroshenko-appoints-member-of-parliament-harbuz-as-governor-of-luhansk-oblast-instead-of-tuka-412967.html|title=Poroshenko appoints member of parliament Harbuz as governor of Luhansk Oblast instead of Tuka|date=2016-04-29|accessdate=2016-05-13 |df=dmy-all}}</ref><ref name=\"Ukraine Today\">{{cite web|url=http://uatoday.tv/politics/poroshenko-appoints-new-luhansk-governor-641069.html|title=Poroshenko appoints new Luhansk governor \u2013 read on \u2013 uatoday.tv|publisher=[[Ukraine Today]]|date=2016-04-30 |df=dmy-all}}</ref><ref name=\"ria\">{{cite web|url=http://ria.ru/incidents/20151007/1298369485.html|title=RF IC opened a case against a deputy of the Parliament of Ukraine Anton Gerashchenko |publisher=[[RIA Novosti]]|date=2015-10-07|accessdate=2016-05-13 |df=dmy-all}}</ref><ref name=\"TCH\">{{cite web |title=TSN 28 Feb 2016 |author= |date=28 Feb 2016 |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=43OSrSl1GcI&t=3093 |publisher={{interlanguage link multi|TSN Ukraine|uk|\u0422\u0421\u041d|vertical-align=sup}} |accessdate=15 May 2016|language=Ukrainian |df=dmy-all}}</ref><ref name=\"thedailybeast20160512\">{{cite web|url=http://www.thedailybeast.com/articles/2016/05/12/ukraine-tries-to-terrify-journalists-who-cover-the-war.html|title=Ukraine Tries to Terrify Journalists Who Cover the War|publisher=[[The Daily Beast]]|date=2016-05-12|accessdate=2016-05-13 |df=dmy-all}}</ref><ref name=\"censorbook\">{{cite web |title = \u0426\u0435\u043d\u0442\u0440 \"\u041c\u0438\u0440\u043e\u0442\u0432\u043e\u0440\u0435\u0446\" \u043f\u0440\u0435\u043a\u0440\u0430\u0449\u0430\u0435\u0442 \u0441\u0432\u043e\u044e \u0434\u0435\u044f\u0442\u0435\u043b\u044c\u043d\u043e\u0441\u0442\u044c \u0432 \u0442\u0435\u043a\u0443\u0449\u0435\u043c \u0444\u043e\u0440\u043c\u0430\u0442\u0435 |trans-title=Center \"Peacemaker\" cease its activities in the current format.|date= 2014-03-16 |url=http://censor.net.ua/blogs/2144/tsentr_quotmirotvoretsquot_prekraschaet_svoyu_deyatelnost_v_tekuschem_formate |publisher={{interlanguage link multi|censor.net|uk|censor.net|vertical-align=sup}} |accessdate=15 May 2016|language=Russian |df=dmy-all}}</ref><ref name=\"clubZ\">{{cite web|url=http://www.clubz.bg/36204-ukrajna_moje_da_sydi_pone_oshte_edin_bylgarski_naemnik |title=Ukraine can sue another Bulgarian mercenary |publisher= club \u2033Z\u2033  |date=2016-03-16 |accessdate=2016-05-16 |language=Bulgarian |df=dmy-all}}</ref><ref name=\"bTV\">{{cite web|url=http://btvnovinite.bg/article/bulgaria/ukrajna-mozhe-da-poiska-da-sadi-ne-edin-a-na-chetirima-balgari.html |title=Ukraine may seek to sue not one but four Bulgarians |publisher= [[bTV (Bulgaria)]]  |date=2016-03-01 |accessdate=2016-05-16 |language=Bulgarian |df=dmy-all}}</ref><ref name=\"ibtimes20160513\">{{cite web|url=http://www.ibtimes.co.uk/ukrainian-hackers-leak-personal-information-thousands-journalists-1559923|title=Ukrainian hackers leak personal information of thousands of journalists|publisher=[[International Business Times]]|date=2015-05-13|accessdate=2016-05-13 |df=dmy-all}}</ref><ref name=\"globalvoices20160511\">{{cite web|url=https://advox.globalvoices.org/2016/05/11/ukrainian-activists-leak-personal-information-of-thousands-of-war-reporters-in-the-donbas/|title=Ukrainian Activists Leak Personal Information of Thousands of War Reporters in the Donbas \u2013 Global Voices Advocacy|date=2016-05-11|publisher=Global Voices Advocacy|accessdate=2016-05-13 |df=dmy-all}}</ref><ref name=\"rt20160512\">{{cite web|url=https://www.rt.com/news/342724-journalists-data-leak-ukraine/|title=Outrage as Ukrainian witch-hunt site leaks personal info of 'terrorist-collaborating journalists' \u2014 RT News|publisher=[[RT (TV network)|RT]]|date=2016-05-12|accessdate=2016-05-13 |df=dmy-all}}</ref><ref name=\"RTTV20151014\">{{cite web|title=Russia steps up Syria air campaign: Jets raise daily action to 88 strikes6 |author= |date=14 Oct 2015 |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=43OSrSl1GcI&t=3093 |publisher=[[RT (TV network)|RT]] |accessdate=15 May 2016|language=Ukrainian |df=dmy-all}}</ref><ref name=\"rt20161007\">{{cite web|url=https://www.rt.com/news/317849-ukrainian-russia-isis-revenge/|title=Top Ukraine official backs idea 'to help ISIS take revenge on Russian soldiers in Syria' \u2014 RT News|date=2016-10-07|publisher=[[RT (TV network)|RT]] |accessdate=2016-05-13 |df=dmy-all}}</ref><ref name=\"MT\">{{cite web|url=http://www.themoscowtimes.com/news/article/russian-investigative-committee-opens-criminal-case-against-putin-accuser/537727.html|title=Russian Investigative Committee Opens Criminal Case Against Putin Accuser|publisher=[[The Moscow Times]]|date=2015-10-08|accessdate=2016-05-13 |df=dmy-all}}</ref><ref name=\"KP\">{{cite web|url=http://www.kp.ru/daily/26442/3313110/|title=\u0423\u043a\u0440\u0430\u0438\u043d\u0441\u043a\u0438\u0439 \u0434\u0435\u043f\u0443\u0442\u0430\u0442 \u0413\u0435\u0440\u0430\u0449\u0435\u043d\u043a\u043e \u043f\u0440\u0435\u0434\u043b\u043e\u0436\u0438\u043b \u0438\u0437\u0431\u0438\u0440\u0430\u0442\u0435\u043b\u044f\u043c \u043f\u043e\u043c\u043e\u0447\u044c \u0442\u0435\u0440\u0440\u04